name: SWAJAN SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT AND HEALTH EDUCATION SAMITI

address: 223- Opposite Padmini Palace Hotel , Kharbuja Mandi, M.D Road,

briefDescription: Swajan Social Development & Health Education Samiti (SSDHES) is a voluntary and non-profitable organization. It was registered under Rajasthan Society Registration Act on 25th, June, 2010 and pursuing activities in the field of community development by sensitization and promoting people on various developmental issues in a capability to work in all over Rajasthan. Swajan believes in a collective and coordinated strategy wherein it involves the efforts of various individuals, groups, NGOs and CBOs in the direction of development of the target population.
